# Real -Time Document Editor рџ“ќ

## Project Overview

 Real -Time Documnet Editor  is a web-based document editing application that allows users to write, edit, format, and manage text documents directly in the
browser. The editor provides features similar to modern online editors like Google Docs, allowing users to apply formatting such as bold, italic, underline, lists, and more.
The application also supports **word counting, document saving, PDF export, and auto-save functionality**, making it a useful productivity tool for writing notes,
documents, and reports.This project was developed as part of a **Full Stack Web Development internship** project.

## Features рџљЂ
### Text Formatting

* Bold text formatting
* Italic text formatting
* Underline text formatting
* Bullet list creation

### Document Editing

* Real-time text editing
* Content editable editor interface
* Clean and responsive UI

### Document Management

* Save documents using Local Storage
* Open previously saved documents
* Clear editor content

### Export Options

* Export document as PDF
* Download written content

### Additional Functionalities

* Word counter
* Auto-save feature
* Responsive design
* Simple toolbar interface

